{"tid":1538970,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好地地教人跳繩咪好囉，做乜做民賤聯","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:50:43.000Z","uid":216002,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"45cd3e4c50bbec739ce55f25167ec64a2ef436cc","tid":1538970,"uid":216002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/04/162149_6dc0393f428f604e322ac1023aa478cd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F04%2F162149_6dc0393f428f604e322ac1023aa478cd.png&h=42dd3493&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/04/162150_7939192d148f6c26b2503a9f36d0d7d9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F04%2F162150_7939192d148f6c26b2503a9f36d0d7d9.png&h=c405aa7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢條友 平時對政治冷感 依家先留抽水  冇啦啦對呢3個月嘅事表態 係咪賺唔夠要做民賤聯 kol都幫唔到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過 你咁想紅 就幫你一把啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4hOBx4p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4hOBx4p.png&h=386933d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mmOqrpq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmmOqrpq.png&h=45655b58&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UpHbmXM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUpHbmXM.png&h=50a330d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4z2yAhN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4z2yAhN.png&h=cd5b36db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYhChv8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYhChv8.png&h=e8313b8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/We2yAhP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWe2yAhP.png&h=c7a1ccdf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UXuMVhQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUXuMVhQ.png&h=b30a79cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EpSZvRb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEpSZvRb.png&h=b3046f6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到依家有人屌佢 佢就咁講野 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fiBx4D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fiBx4D.png&h=51c9b638&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7JiRmXZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7JiRmXZ.png&h=ddb614e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早知當初又何必當初<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  依家扮慘都冇用！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢仲public緊 歡迎大家大大力咁屌佢</span></span>"},{"pid":"cc4ac175b707a99bbc711ed3a9ce4d4277792cbd","tid":1538970,"uid":2479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:27:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n9月8 要人</span><br />\n<br />\n全世界9月8號出俾佢睇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538569</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7c90fc07eba33a2b46c147632684a9482ac4f5f5","tid":1538970,"uid":216002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:27:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53062092868caeee5d87e8d79ed92b281afda275","tid":1538970,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:28:36.000Z","msg":"【831 太子站目擊者立法會見記者】<br />\n-有一個人失蹤<br />\n-有機會有一個人死左 比警察打左半個鐘 嘔白泡 差佬見佢冇反應 之後冇打 二三十分鐘後由消防員 非救護人員 送走 完全冇反應<br />\n-差佬同佢地講想屌佢地係正常<br />\n-有被捕人士係警署被非禮 (摸胸)<br />\n-係警署去廁所時不能關門 而當時有其他性別既警員在場<br />\n-有日本人被捕 警方拒絕比佢聯繫大使館<br />\n-目擊者話傷者係送去瑪嘉烈唔係廣華<br />\n-速龍落電梯 踩住市民背部甚至頭部落"},{"pid":"e0a1c8a4fda513d1a6f38de4dc501edf7411058c","tid":1538970,"uid":216002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08